derivation: from G1 (ἀνυπότακτος) (as a negative particle) and a presumed derivative of G5293 (ἀνυπότακτος);
kjv_def: disobedient, that is not put under, unruly
strongs_def: unsubdued, i.e. insubordinate (in fact or temper)
outline:
1. not made subject, unsubjected
  2. that cannot be subjected to control, disobedient, unruly, refractory
